 <h4>Solution by forward Euler method (explicit)</h4>
 <p>For that purpose, the II order equation is reduced to thefollowing system of I order equations</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>θ′</var>
   =
   <var>ω</var>
  </span>
  and
  <span class="eq">
   <var>ω′</var>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>g</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    <var>l</var>
   </span>
   ·
   <b>sin</b>
